<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sast-Sonar Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { background: #121212; color: #e0e0e0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
        .card { background: #1e1e1e; border: 1px solid #333; color: white; border-radius: 15px; }
        .status-up { color: #00ff00; }
        .btn-custom { background: #6200ee; color: white; border-radius: 10px; }
        .btn-custom:hover { background: #3700b3; color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">🚀 Sast-Sonar Project</h1>
            <p class="lead">Servidor Monitoreado en Tiempo Real</p>
            <span class="badge bg-success">Status: ONLINE</span>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card p-4 h-100 shadow">
                    <h3>📊 Monitoreo</h3>
                    <p>Accede a los paneles de control internos:</p>
                    <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                        <a href="/metrics" class="btn btn-outline-light" target="_blank">Ver Métricas Raw</a>
                        <a href="http://34.51.110.74:3001" class="btn btn-custom" target="_blank">Ir a Grafana</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card p-4 h-100 shadow">
                    <h3>🛠️ Detalles del Stack</h3>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li>✅ <strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js + Express</li>
                        <li>✅ <strong>DevOps:</strong> Docker + GitHub Actions</li>
                        <li>✅ <strong>Observabilidad:</strong> Prometheus + Grafana</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>